comments: I did realise that each color had a different spelling; so while the shape might have been the same the spelling was slightly different and  remembering which spelling went with which color is something that i really struggled with. I dont feel like i found any aspects to be easy to be honest, i found each aspect to be quite hard. I just used my brain to try and remember as best as i could, i wasnt aware that i could have taken notes and even then i felt like the task went by to quickly for me to even try to attempt that
